headline: Booking.com's 2025 Sustainable Travel Research Reveals Growing Awareness of Tourism's Impact on Communities
summary: Since first conducting research on consumer attitudes about travelling more sustainably in 2016, Booking.com has surveyed nearly 230,000 travellers in 35 markets.
